cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper focuses on vision-based lane keeping assistance using grayscale images from a single front view camera. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper utilizes convolutional neural networks (CNN) for policy learning via imitation learning. 
3. cs.RO (Robotics): The paper aims to develop a lane keeping assistance system for a vehicle. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses machine learning techniques for developing an intelligent system for lane keeping assistance. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper evaluates the learned policy in closed-loop simulated environments, demonstrating the control aspect of the system.
